author: Chris Yuscavage
title: Tony Romo Said “See You in February” to Tom Brady After the Patriots Beat the Cowboys
text:
Tony Romo seems to be pretty confident that the Cowboys are going to go to the Super Bowl . He talked about it back in April . He talked about it again in July . And after the Patriots knocked off the Cowboys on Sunday to drop them to 2-3 on the season, he talked about it again while congratulating Tom Brady on a win.
“See you in February,” Romo said as he walked by Brady.
Brady didn’t really acknowledge him. But if one thing’s clear, it’s that Romo really, really, really thinks the Cowboys are destined to make a Super Bowl run this season. You buying it?
 .
